thread.title_full: Rubber Stamp Champ reviewed by CCKOM

author: CCKOM
title: CCKOM
text:
I had the wonderful privilege of working with Carol to design a series of five stamps, each representing a different species of Sea Turtle. We are a small nature center in Boca Raton, FL, and we needed these stamps to help round out a scavenger hunt-style program we are holding as part of Sea Turtle Awareness Month. The stamps came out beautifully, and we are looking forward to our upcoming program.
Thank you Carol and everyone at Rubber Stamp Champ for your excellent customer service, quick turn-around and wonderful products.
Save the Sea Turtles!
